clutch <item> - Carry something in your clutches.
dchat - Version of tell that lets you talk to all your guild members.
edchat - Guild channel emote.
dcmds - A list of dragon commands.
declare <form> - This command sets your dragon form.
redeclare <form> - At age 19, you can change your dragon form.
The magics involved will regenerate 2 years of life.
demotes - A list of dragon emotes.
dhist - This shows a history of all communications on the Dragon channel.
dragonhelp or dhelp <command> You can get more info on 'align' and 'powers'.
dragonlong <string> - Sets what people see when they look at you.
dtimers - Lists out your spell timers.
dwho - Version of "who" that only shows your guild members.

For more info, you can dhelp 'basics', 'align', or 'powers'
